{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Those of you who know me know how passionate I am"},{"time":3000,"text":"about opening the space frontier."},{"time":5000,"text":"So when I had the chance to give the world's expert in gravity"},{"time":9000,"text":"the experience of zero gravity, it was incredible."},{"time":12000,"text":"And I want to tell you that story."},{"time":14000,"text":"I first met him through the Archon X PRIZE for Genomics."},{"time":19000,"text":"It's a competition we're holding, the second X PRIZE,"},{"time":22000,"text":"for the first team to sequence 100 human genomes in 10 days."},{"time":25000,"text":"We have something called the Genome 100 --"},{"time":27000,"text":"100 individuals we're sequencing as part of that."},{"time":30000,"text":"Craig Venter chairs that event."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"And I met Professor Hawking,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and he said his dream was to travel into space."},{"time":36000,"text":"And I said, \"I can't take you there,"},{"time":38000,"text":"but I can take you into weightlessness into zero-g."},{"time":41000,"text":"And he said, on the spot, \"Absolutely, yes.\""},{"time":43000,"text":"Well, the only way to experience zero-g on Earth"},{"time":46000,"text":"is actually with parabolic flight, weightless flight."},{"time":49000,"text":"You take an airplane, you fly over the top, you're weightless for 25 seconds."},{"time":53000,"text":"Come back down, you weigh twice as much."},{"time":55000,"text":"You do it again and again."},{"time":57000,"text":"You can get eight, 10 minutes of weightlessness --"},{"time":58000,"text":"how NASA's trained their astronauts for so long."},{"time":61000,"text":"We set out to do this."},{"time":63000,"text":"It took us 11 years to become operational."},{"time":65000,"text":"And we announced that we were going to fly Stephen Hawking."},{"time":67000,"text":"We had one government agency and one company aircraft operator say,"},{"time":71000,"text":"you're crazy, don't do that, you're going kill the guy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"And he wanted to go."},{"time":76000,"text":"We worked hard to get all the permissions."},{"time":79000,"text":"And six months later, we sat down at Kennedy Space Center."},{"time":82000,"text":"We had a press conference,"},{"time":84000,"text":"we announced our intent to do one zero-g parabola,"},{"time":88000,"text":"give him 25 seconds of zero-g."},{"time":91000,"text":"And if it went really well, we might do three parabolas."},{"time":94000,"text":"Well, we asked him why he wanted to go up and do this."},{"time":99000,"text":"And what he said, for me, was very moving."},{"time":101000,"text":"He said, \"Life on Earth is at an ever-increasing risk"},{"time":103000,"text":"of being wiped out by disaster ..."},{"time":105000,"text":"I think the human race doesn't have a future if it doesn't go into space."},{"time":108000,"text":"I therefore want to encourage public interest in space.\""},{"time":112000,"text":"We took him out to the Kennedy Space Center,"},{"time":115000,"text":"up inside the NASA vehicle, into the back of the zero-g airplane."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"We had about 20 people who made donations --"},{"time":127000,"text":"we raised $150,000 in donations for children's charities --"},{"time":130000,"text":"who flew with us."},{"time":132000,"text":"A few TEDsters here."},{"time":134000,"text":"We set up a whole ER."},{"time":136000,"text":"We had four emergency room doctors and two nurses on board the airplane."},{"time":139000,"text":"We were monitoring his PO2 of his blood, his heart rate, his blood pressure."},{"time":143000,"text":"We had everything all set in case of an emergency;"},{"time":146000,"text":"God knows, you don't want to hurt this world-renowned expert."},{"time":149000,"text":"We took off from the shuttle landing facility,"},{"time":152000,"text":"where the shuttle takes off and lands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154000,"text":"And my partner Byron Lichtenberg and I"},{"time":157000,"text":"carefully suspended him into zero-g."},{"time":160000,"text":"Once he was there, [we] let him go"},{"time":162000,"text":"to experience what weightlessness was truly like."},{"time":166000,"text":"And after that first parabola, you know,"},{"time":170000,"text":"the doc said everything is great. He was smiling, and we said go."},{"time":174000,"text":"So we did a second parabola."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"And a third."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"We actually floated an apple in homage to Sir Isaac Newton"},{"time":192000,"text":"because Professor Hawking holds the same chair at Cambridge"},{"time":195000,"text":"that Isaac Newton did."},{"time":197000,"text":"And we did a fourth, and a fifth and a sixth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"And a seventh and an eighth."},{"time":204000,"text":"And this man does not look like a 65-year-old wheelchair-bound man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"He was so happy."},{"time":210000,"text":"We are living on a precious jewel,"},{"time":213000,"text":"and it's during our lifetime that we're moving off this planet."},{"time":216000,"text":"Please join us in this epic adventure."},{"time":218000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}